title: Interpret this capacitor?
message:
.1u_0201_25V6-K 
so I’m good with .1uf, 0201
but do you think the rest means 25.6V and 10% tolerance?

title: Interpret this capacitor?
message:
25V is the nominal voltage.
Tolerance has no importance here.
Apart of nominal capacitance and voltage, the size is last you need to match.
